								label(for='validate_phone') Телефон
								input.form-control.form-control-lg#validate_phone(maxlength="18" value='' type='tel' placeholder='Ваш Телефон' name='tel' pattern='^(\+?\d[- .]*){7,13}' required)
						.form-check.my-5
							.row.align-items-center
								.col-lg-6.col-md-12
									input.form-check-input#validate_Check.mr-2(type='checkbox' value='' required)
									input.form-check-input.d-none(type='checkbox' name='spam')
									label.form-check-label.ml-2(for='validate_Check') Я даю согласие на обработку персональных данных
